---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service – Stop Sueing Valve" description="Terms of service for Stop Sueing Valve website and newsletter.">
	<article class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
		<header class="mb-12 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 tracking-tight mb-4">
				Terms of Service
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-stone-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				By using this website or subscribing to our newsletter, you agree to these terms.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-stone-600 space-y-6 text-left">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">About this website</h2>
				<p>
					Stop Sueing Valve ("we", "us", "our") operates stopsueingvalve.com. This website provides information about collective actions and lawsuits against Valve Corporation and options for opting out of default-opt-in lawsuits. We are an independent information resource and are not affiliated with Valve Corporation or any law firm.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Information purposes only</h2>
				<p>
					The content on this website is provided for informational purposes only. It does not constitute legal advice, and you should not rely on it as such. We make no guarantees about the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the information provided. If you need legal advice, consult a qualified attorney in your jurisdiction.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Newsletter subscription</h2>
				<p>
					By subscribing to our newsletter, you agree to:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li>Provide accurate and valid email information</li>
					<li>Receive emails related to the topics you selected (Consumer Updates, Developer Updates, Lawsuit Updates, New Lawsuits)</li>
					<li>Our <a href="/privacy" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline">Privacy Policy</a> regarding how we handle your data</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-2">
					You may unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link in any email or by contacting us at <a href="mailto:contact@stopsueingvalve.com" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline">contact@stopsueingvalve.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Acceptable use</h2>
				<p>
					When using this website and our newsletter service, you agree not to:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
					<li>Use the service for any unlawful purpose</li>
					<li>Provide false information when subscribing</li>
					<li>Attempt to disrupt or compromise the security of our systems</li>
					<li>Use the information provided to harass any company, individual, or organization</li>
					<li>Redistribute our content for commercial purposes without permission</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">No harassment</h2>
				<p>
					We explicitly do not support or condone harassment of any company, law firm, individual, or organization. Our goal is to provide factual information and opt-out options. Users who engage in harassment based on information from this site do so against our stated principles.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Intellectual property</h2>
				<p>
					This website and its content, including the logo, were created with the assistance of AI tools. The content is provided freely for personal, non-commercial use. You may share links to this website and quote reasonable portions of our content with attribution.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">External links</h2>
				<p>
					This website may contain links to external websites (e.g., lawsuit filing sites, court documents, official opt-out forms). We are not responsible for the content or practices of these external sites. Use them at your own discretion.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Limitation of liability</h2>
				<p>
					To the fullest extent permitted by law, we disclaim all liability for any damages arising from your use of this website or reliance on its content. This includes, but is not limited to, missing opt-out deadlines, misunderstanding legal procedures, or any decisions made based on information provided here.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Changes to these terms</h2>
				<p>
					We may update these terms from time to time. The current version will always be on this page. Continued use of the website or newsletter after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms. Last updated: January 2026.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Contact</h2>
				<p>
					If you have questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@stopsueingvalve.com" class="text-stone-800 underline hover:no-underline">contact@stopsueingvalve.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<p class="text-sm text-stone-500 pt-4 text-center">
				Contact: <a href="mailto:contact@stopsueingvalve.com" class="text-stone-700 underline hover:no-underline">contact@stopsueingvalve.com</a>
			</p>
		</div>
	</article>
</Layout>
